{"tid":1442653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"共產黨有咩唔好呀！？","createTime":"2019-08-11T04:23:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T09:55:44.000Z","uid":166129,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"d8b6d99f8521bdfc429ebefd8f70ce4f02538bbc","tid":1442653,"uid":166129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:23:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>大家遇上呢個問題會點答?</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發覺好多藍絲/中間派都真心覺得<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>&quot;共產黨都唔係好差 / 比以前好左&quot; </strong></span>意思大慨係&quot;服從&quot;都無所謂啦<br />\n<br />\n小小愚見<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">文宣係咪應該多D向呢個方向發展?</span> <br />\n(感覺以家80%以上都係講林鄭 高官 黑警)<br />\n<br />\n因為你比佢地睇&quot;警察做左咩過份既事&quot;  佢地只會覺得你地唔搞事 警察點會打你射你<br />\n<br />\n佢地係真心唔明<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: brown;\">共產黨有咩唔好</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">再貼一張近期覺得幾得意既圖..</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m8SrEJ1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm8SrEJ1.jpg&h=a40000b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10593ba34b7a853e967aaa5501227514a6d345c1","tid":1442653,"uid":185448,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:24:25.000Z","msg":"咁返大陸住好唔好?"},{"pid":"959daabcf839e56f829e4207df85f734f36c9d2b","tid":1442653,"uid":221265,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:27:37.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">721元朗恐襲</span></strong></span></div><br />\n警黑合作, 警署落閘, <br />\n999唔通,無人落charge<br />\n<br />\n721元朗恐襲第22日<br />\n無人落charge <br />\n無警停職<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無忘721<br />\n記者請日日追問插問</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家copy and paste pls<br />\n每日改第xx日<br />\n<br />\nKeep push t